Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.98,0:01:33.82,*Default,?NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個半徑5公里的人工島上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.00,0:01:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預定建造地下2層 地上8層的圓形廣場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.83,0:01:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外還有一座隱蔽的娛樂中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.83,0:01:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.11,0:01:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤潮 也就是受了浮游生物的影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.64,0:01:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是伴隨著開發産生的正常現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.35,0:01:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要任何擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.16,0:01:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然不需要任何擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.49,0:01:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果發生甚麼狀況的話由你們負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.56,0:02:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想沒飯吃的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.33,0:02:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就給我好好檢討一下對策方案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.40,0:02:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海~在哭泣 天空~在哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.84,0:02:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的未來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.31,0:02:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.04,0:02:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在擔心那已經沒有希望的未來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.81,0:02:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從奠基開始建設到現在飛快流逝的幾年裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.89,0:02:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克服無數困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.89,0:02:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們終於迎來了這座東京TOREJYA完工的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.99,0:02:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著即將打開這扇夢想的樂園之門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.11,0:02:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5 4 3 2 1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.56,0:03:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\pos(300,320)}第 15 話    海·泳裝·大海獸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲~真是個好地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.32,0:03:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 恭平君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.01,0:03:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 虧你還是個年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.89,0:03:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 快看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是心情舒暢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.07,0:03:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.41,0:03:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你們2個已經開始熱情高漲了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是有男生做伴好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.69,0:03:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁野先生能來實在是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.01,0:03:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 應該感謝你邀請我來放鬆一下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.41,0:03:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到這裡 賽小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.27,0:03:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不認爲我們大人也應該在一起好好享受一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.77,0:03:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 聽起來不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.37,0:03:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊昂 上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.02,0:04:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.00,0:04:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我明明都跟他說了危險了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萊昂 COME ON
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要來報仇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.80,0:04:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 退縮就不是男人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.43,0:04:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 恭平君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.62,0:04:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.93,0:04:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你往哪里打啊 你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.31,0:04:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 賽不玩嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.59,0:04:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.79,0:04:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在情況如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.05,0:04:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前一切順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.65,0:04:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面好像對最新型的遊戲機和餐廳有所不滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.12,0:04:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是最新型的話應該是利用海水的超電磁巨型機吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.17,0:04:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想讓那些在假海水浴場嬉戲的傢夥們看看這些綠色毒藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.59,0:04:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空好高啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.11,0:05:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.59,0:05:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在從網路上收集這裡的秘密情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.75,0:05:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到這裡了就沒必要擺弄甚麼電腦了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是偏見啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.88,0:05:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩這個才是我最大的樂趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.87,0:05:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.06,0:05:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是賽姐你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.01,0:05:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件泳裝真是超級沒品位啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.01,0:05:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.69,0:05:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.73,0:05:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件泳裝設計得真是不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.13,0:05:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.87,0:05:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也這樣認爲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.91,0:05:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 你是不是模特兒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.29,0:05:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一說覺得好像在哪里見過你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是女優?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.47,0:05:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是來奉承我的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.30,0:05:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎 真是難以置信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.46,0:05:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.22,0:05:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠在今天被邀請來這裡一定是有甚麼特殊身份的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.10,0:05:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你們幹甚麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.90,0:05:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是你妹妹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.43,0:06:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件泳裝也很適合她啊 很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.45,0:06:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥幫你檢查暑假作業吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.24,0:06:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.25,0:06:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喬 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.75,0:06:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微下手重了點 好像昏過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了甚麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.25,0:06:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.28,0:06:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 好久不見啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.92,0:06:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我接下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.15,0:06:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把30個街道的黑幫分子全部消滅就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.18,0:06:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點是郊外的購物中心 OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.48,0:06:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的超級拍檔半天就可以清理完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.26,0:06:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.98,0:06:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.73,0:06:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽 對方在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼急的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.61,0:06:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天你去當一下市里的自警團保鏢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.18,0:06:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前好好放鬆一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.45,0:06:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來搞個惡作劇把那三個人從招待名單上刪掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.32,0:07:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老實點 做小孩子做該做的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.77,0:07:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭平 你也去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都阻止不了我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.18,0:07:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 多少歲數了 還做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.67,0:07:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點常識都沒有嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.31,0:07:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.57,0:07:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.69,0:08:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.27,0:08:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經冰過了 請用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.55,0:08:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 賽小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.11,0:08:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來恭平君 有事想拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.19,0:08:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是我爺爺的朋友聚餐的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.71,0:08:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吃的東西很挑剔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.73,0:08:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必展示下你的手藝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.51,0:08:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個沒問題 要做些甚麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.24,0:08:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最得意的甜點1000份就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.60,0:08:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1000人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.41,0:08:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.34,0:08:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.88,0:08:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 恭平君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.32,0:08:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你年輕啊 熬夜吧熬夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.40,0:08:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個甜點我也要吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.90,0:08:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼好吃嗎 我也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭平太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 一點都不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.65,0:08:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 開玩笑的 玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.54,0:08:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.21,0:08:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.49,0:09:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不是馬達的聲音 是別的類型的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得沒有再次檢查的必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.26,0:09:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想只是機器還磨合得不太好而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.85,0:09:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我會登記在日常列表上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.62,0:09:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我弄錯了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.08,0:09:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.58,0:09:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冰的很舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.32,0:09:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬真是不可思議啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.91,0:09:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和第一次見面的時候一樣完全沒有改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.96,0:09:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自來到這個國家以來一直遇到些令人驚奇的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會到今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.93,0:10:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得走到今天有點像做夢一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.78,0:10:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都這樣就好了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.71,0:10:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.22,0:10:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.17,0:10:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 偶爾會想在遇到我前喬是甚麼樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.34,0:10:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直覺得你是不是每天都在戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.29,0:10:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是喬不管是工作的時候還是不工作的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺都在跟甚麼戰鬥著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.68,0:10:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外你好像甚麼都不感興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.34,0:10:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 這樣也無所謂啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.06,0:11:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去戰鬥都是爲了你啊 美谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.67,0:11:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.74,0:11:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲你救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.20,0:11:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?真的這麼想?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.90,0:11:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.16,0:11:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 我想能夠遇到喬真的是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.65,0:12:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 果然這裡超級大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.13,0:12:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬 你在幹甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.03,0:12:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.15,0:12:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了?聽到甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.83,0:12:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.95,0:12:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給客人的通知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.64,0:12:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始東京TOREJYA的所有設備將進行檢修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.88,0:12:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美谷 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.54,0:12:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.90,0:12:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請客人們儘快離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.15,0:13:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且 爲了以防萬一請客人絕對不要抽煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.50,0:13:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香煙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.36,0:13:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因爲這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.23,0:13:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麼 好噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.50,0:13:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個附近發生過謎一般的石油運輸船相撞事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.46,0:13:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 所以禁止抽煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.52,0:13:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點個火的話這裡就會變成像平底鍋一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.97,0:13:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.46,0:13:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼叫爲了以防萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道危險應該說得更清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.00,0:13:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出真相的話 就只會造成混亂而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.64,0:13:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也趕快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.38,0:13:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.26,0:13:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 我還想玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.86,0:13:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防油護欄60%展開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.23,0:13:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是油的流動比想像中的快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.71,0:13:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,載人巴士已經到達 開始避難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.81,0:13:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請按秩序上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.92,0:13:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要牽好小孩子的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.40,0:14:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.06,0:14:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.80,0:14:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 你們也稍微來熱鬧一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.97,0:14:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是一個人都沒有 沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.15,0:14:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易從我老爹的口袋裡偷出來的全場遊玩的票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也該稍微感謝下我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 看看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.97,0:14:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼 有甚麼有趣的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.43,0:14:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼 甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.77,0:14:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.26,0:15:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.93,0:15:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩了 拖車停在對面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.55,0:15:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又沒辦法穿過火牆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.18,0:15:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼辦法都沒有了 不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.49,0:15:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種情況下大家爲甚麼還能這麼冷靜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.43,0:15:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們就先到屋頂上等待救援吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成 快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 有直升機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.12,0:15:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萊昂 會開嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.66,0:15:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.16,0:15:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.14,0:15:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 直升機被...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.35,0:15:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.51,0:15:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章魚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.39,0:15:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 怎麼可能有這麼大的章魚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.39,0:15:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認爲大概是...章魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.53,0:15:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之是怪物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.92,0:15:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不管人命就跑回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.75,0:16:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,載人巴士的駕駛員這樣報告的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.58,0:16:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從那樣的火中救人出來機會渺茫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.06,0:16:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 問題是這個擅忽職守的責任由誰來負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.67,0:16:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.92,0:16:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有過一個反對建設的環境保護團體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說是他們搞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.39,0:16:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.69,0:16:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.09,0:16:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地收集證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在記者會上發佈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.54,0:16:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.89,0:16:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.87,0:16:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.52,0:16:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到你了吧 對...對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.62,0:16:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該不會是墨魚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可不是說冷笑話的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.31,0:16:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦才好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.70,0:16:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是美谷姐今天墨魚吃太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.34,0:16:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以觸怒了墨魚神結果跑出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.05,0:16:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨魚怎麼可能有神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.17,0:17:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲甚麼沒坐上巴士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.74,0:17:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想躲起來玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.83,0:17:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香煙火 一瞬間...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.98,0:17:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火就燒起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.04,0:17:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起火的原因原來是你們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.49,0:17:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因爲你帶我們來所以才會這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.18,0:17:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩人啊 別推到我身上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前還不是很開心嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.67,0:17:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.08,0:17:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 原諒我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.33,0:17:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個東西給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.73,0:17:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬 你想要怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.17,0:17:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 我飛過去了 你就準備好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.75,0:17:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.14,0:17:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把怪物全部幹掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.78,0:18:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.95,0:18:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.07,0:18:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬是故意被甩出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.94,0:18:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.18,0:18:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是爲了穿越火牆 但真是個亂來的傢夥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.34,0:18:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 快點用遙控器把武器庫打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.91,0:18:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 準備原來是指這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.78,0:18:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.34,0:18:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來現在不知道狀況的只有美谷姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.90,0:18:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泄漏的石油已經流進建築物內部了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 我不要死在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.09,0:18:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來救救我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.08,0:18:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 是男人的話就給我挺起胸膛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.20,0:18:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.70,0:18:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬 活著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.03,0:19:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.30,0:19:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去沒完沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.24,0:19:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.98,0:19:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼都看不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.46,0:20:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.71,0:20:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了全變黑了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.76,0:20:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛幫它上過蠟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.92,0:20:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況沒得選擇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.72,0:20:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說喬你這個傢夥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.47,0:20:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 算了 得救了就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.95,0:20:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的JYANGO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.27,0:20:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔你也全黑了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.29,0:20:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好 所有受困的人都已經救出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.25,0:20:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出事的原因目前還在調查中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.77,0:21:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們收到了阻止東京TOREJYA建成的\N環境保護團體可能有所牽連的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.08,0:21:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這個是事實的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.65,0:21:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就構成了無差別大量殺人的犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.93,0:21:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無法饒恕的行爲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.30,0:21:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定徹底把原因...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.01,0:21:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你都沒受傷 真是太好了 立場無君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.44,0:21:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是給你一個人偷偷出去玩的懲罰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.67,0:21:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨魚 墨魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.03,0:21:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 立場無君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.63,0:21:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭平 振作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.15,0:21:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨魚...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.94,0:21:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭平~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.88,0:23:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏在黑暗中正體不明的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.81,0:23:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了抓住那無法辨別是噩夢還是夢幻的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.40,0:23:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬被帶到了異世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.02,0:23:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 爆裂天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.83,0:23:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔境戰鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.06,0:23:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待



